text: Athi Mafazwe (born 13 September 1997) is a South African cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Eastern Province in the 2018 Africa T20 Cup on 14 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Eastern Province cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
